0142, rozwa\u017c zmian\u0119 strategii.<\/li>\n<li><b>Rozmowa z klientem<\/b>: Przygotuj si\u0119 na szczer\u0105 rozmow\u0119 z klientem na temat wprowadzanych strategii, podkre\u015blaj\u0105c, \u017ce obni\u017cenie ceny to czasowy krok, maj\u0105cy na celu zbudowanie silnej obecno\u015bci na rynku.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Pod\u0105\u017caj\u0105c za tymi wskaz\u00f3wkami, mo\u017cesz znacznie zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 swoj\u0105 sprzeda\u017c w ci\u0105gu najbli\u017cszych kilku tygodni i przygotowa\u0107 produkt do d\u0142ugoterminowego sukcesu na Amazonie. <b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><b>Jak zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c produkt\u00f3w na Amazonie?<\/b> Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak sprawi\u0107, aby Tw\u00f3j pr<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5814,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5813","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5813"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5813"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5813\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5814"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5813"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json